- ./script.sh
- Make devops.txt Read-Only

- chmod 640 notes.txt
- Create Directory With 755 Permission
- mkdir project
- chmod 755 project

ğŸ¯ What I Learned
- Linux file access depends on permissions
- Numeric permissions simplify access control
- Execute permission is required to run scripts
- ls -l helps verify permissions
